attributes.name: Lacy Handbag S
attributes.description: To celebrate the 55th anniversary AIGNER created a very special model. The luxurious Lacy range of bags reminds you of festive moments. Thanks to its top-quality leather look, this bag shines in full glory. The striking gold melted A-logo buckle rounds off this extravagant and stylish design. Now available at the official AIGNER online shop.
